description: This home qualifies for our MAKE AN OFFER SALES EVENT! Located just 20 minutes from downtown Oklahoma City, the “Heart of the Heartland,” Harrah, is one of Oklahoma City’s fastest growing suburbs. Our premier community Brush Creek offers residents the perfect mixture of urban and rural living with rolling hills and an abundance of greenery all while lying in close proximity to Tinker AFB, Kickapoo Turnpike, Interstate 40, Interstate 44, Rose State College, Oklahoma Baptist University, The University of Oklahoma, and so much more! Harrah is also the home of a brand new top-notch SSM Health facility. The Harrah school system consistently ranks as one of the top school systems in Oklahoma, with students scoring in the upper rankings for state as well as national achievements. The Harrah community is known for putting on numerous festivals at the Harrah Heritage Park. Our Scissortail collection homes, are packed with energy efficiency features and built in tornado safety features while still offering beautiful eye-catching interior finishes.
